description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Breathwork for Deep and Restful Sleep - Simple Breathing Exercise to Help You Relax' from the channel Kirsten McCormick.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This guided breathwork practice is designed to help you prepare for sleep by using deeply soothing and conscious connected breaths to experience a restful and better night's sleep. Clear your space, turn your lights down low, and follow along with this practice to allow your mind to shift gears. Let your body and mind sink into your sleep....
